*Limited Retail Penetration (Historically):* Apple has invested in retail s=
tores in China=E2=80=99s major cities, but its reach into smaller cities wa=
s historically limited. Local brands, by contrast, have sprawling distribut=
ion networks across urban and rural areas. While Apple has expanded its onl=
ine presence and reseller network, this earlier lack of penetration in tier=
-3/4 cities meant it missed the chance to capture customers outside the big=
