What remains is one final bundle: the creation and substantiation of an ide=
a. To use myself as an example, I have plenty of ideas, and thanks to the I=
nternet, the ability to distribute them around the globe; however, I still =
need to write them down, just as an artist needs to create an image, or a m=
usician needs to write a song. What is becoming increasingly clear, though,=
 is that this too is a bottleneck that is on the verge of being removed.

This is exactly what that second report in particular is demonstrating. The=
 ideas are mine, but the substantiation is AI, and not only is it pretty da=
mn good, it's also the worst it is ever going to be.

